        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". In order to place the scene of the denials in Caiaphas’ presence, it has been discovered, although John gives not the slightest indication of it, that Annas and Caiaphas inhabited ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
