        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (Euth. Zigabenus, Casaubon, Ebrard, Lange, Lichtenstein, Riggenbach, Hengstenberg, Godet). In order, also, to assign the hearing of 19–21 to Caiaphas, some have taken ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
